  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nI ran into a funny issue. \r\n\r\nIf you notice the following screenshot, the actual command that I had typed was `accounts`, but it seems that brownie console doesn't respect user's color settings. (my guess is that command colors are separately hardcoded to display a certain color). \r\n\r\n<img width=\"858\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-05-24 at 3 32 43 PM\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8398696/119400090-acd2f980-bca7-11eb-9b06-c7f9df980fb1.png\">\r\n",
